[32m+[m[32m---[m
[32m+[m[32mtitle: 'Non-Template Message'[m
[32m+[m[32mdescription: 'Send direct WhatsApp messages with text, media, and rich content without templates'[m
[32m+[m[32micon: 'message'[m
[32m+[m[32m---[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m<Tip>[m
[32m+[m[32mSend instant WhatsApp messages directly to your customers without requiring pre-approved templates. Perfect for quick responses, customer support, and media sharing during ongoing conversations.[m
[32m+[m[32m</Tip>[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mThe Send Non-Template Message API enables you to send immediate WhatsApp messages including text, images, videos, audio, and documents. This is ideal for customer support scenarios and ongoing conversations where template approval is not required.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## Overview[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mThe Send Non-Template Message API enables you to:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- Send instant text messages with URL previews[m
[32m+[m[32m- Share images, videos, and documents with captions[m
[32m+[m[32m- Send audio files and voice messages[m
[32m+[m[32m- Organize messages with custom labels for analytics[m
[32m+[m[32m- Respond quickly in customer support scenarios[m
[32m+[m[32m- Continue conversations without template restrictions[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## Send Non-Template Message[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mSend various types of WhatsApp messages directly to a specific phone number without requiring pre-approved templates.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### Endpoint[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m[32mPOST https://api.insightssystem.com/api:U9ztporN/send/message[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### Authentication[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m<Warning>[m
[32m+[m[32mAll API requests require authentication using your API key. Never share your API keys in client-side code or public repositories.[m
[32m+[m[32m</Warning>[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mInclude your API key in all requests using Bearer authentication:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m<CodeGroup>[m
[32m+[m[32m```bash[m
[32m+[m[32mAuthorization: Bearer YOUR_API_KEY[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m```javascript[m
[32m+[m[32mheaders: {[m
[32m+[m[32m  'Authorization': 'Bearer YOUR_API_KEY',[m
[32m+[m[32m  'Content-Type': 'application/json'[m
[32m+[m[32m}[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m[32m</CodeGroup>[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### Request Body[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m<ParamField body="to" type="string" required>[m
[32m+[m[32m  The recipient's phone number in international format with country code (e.g., "+15551234567").[m
[32m+[m[32m</ParamField>[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m<ParamField body="type" type="string" required>[m
[32m+[m[32m  The type of message to send. Must be one of: `text`, `image`, `video`, `audio`, `document`.[m
[32m+[m[32m</ParamField>[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m<ParamField body="api_key" type="string" required>[m
[32m+[m[32m  Your API key for authentication (also required in request body).[m
[32m+[m[32m</ParamField>[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m<ParamField body="recipient_type" type="string" default="individual">[m
[32m+[m[32m  The type of recipient. Always use "individual" for single recipients.[m
[32m+[m[32m</ParamField>[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m<ParamField body="messaging_product" type="string" default="whatsapp">[m
[32m+[m[32m  The messaging platform. Always use "whatsapp".[m
[32m+[m[32m</ParamField>[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m<ParamField body="labels" type="array" optional>[m
[32m+[m[32m  Array of strings for message categorization and analytics (e.g., ["support", "urgent"]).[m
[32m+[m[32m</ParamField>[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### Message Type-Specific Parameters[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m<Tabs>[m
[32m+[m[32m  <Tab title="Text Messages">[m
[32m+[m[32m    <ParamField body="text" type="object" required>[m
[32m+[m[32m      Text message configuration[m
[32m+[m[32m      <Expandable title="Text Properties">[m
[32m+[m[32m        <ParamField body="body" type="string" required>[m
[32m+[m[32m          The text content of the message (max 4096 characters)[m
[32m+[m[32m        </ParamField>[m
[32m+[m[32m        <ParamField body="preview_url" type="boolean" default="false">[m
[32m+[m[32m          Whether to show URL previews for links in the message[m
[32m+[m[32m        </ParamField>[m
[32m+[m[32m      </Expandable>[m
[32m+[m[32m    </ParamField>[m
[32m+[m[32m  </Tab>[m
[32m+[m[41m  [m
[32m+[m[32m  <Tab title="Image Messages">[m
[32m+[m[32m    <ParamField body="image" type="object" required>[m
[32m+[m[32m      Image message configuration[m
[32m+[m[32m      <Expandable title="Image Properties">[m
[32m+[m[32m        <ParamField body="link" type="string" required>[m
[32m+[m[32m          Public URL to the image file (JPG, JPEG, PNG)[m
[32m+[m[32m        </ParamField>[m
[32m+[m[32m        <ParamField body="caption" type="string" optional>[m
[32m+[m[32m          Text caption for the image (max 1024 characters)[m
[32m+[m[32m        </ParamField>[m
[32m+[m[32m      </Expandable>[m
[32m+[m[32m    </ParamField>[m
[32m+[m[32m  </Tab>[m
[32m+[m[41m  [m
[32m+[m[32m  <Tab title="Video Messages">[m
[32m+[m[32m    <ParamField body="video" type="object" required>[m
[32m+[m[32m      Video message configuration[m
[32m+[m[32m      <Expandable title="Video Properties">[m
[32m+[m[32m        <ParamField body="link" type="string" required>[m
[32m+[m[32m          Public URL to the video file (MP4, 3GPP)[m
[32m+[m[32m        </ParamField>[m
[32m+[m[32m        <ParamField body="caption" type="string" optional>[m
[32m+[m[32m          Text caption for the video (max 1024 characters)[m
[32m+[m[32m        </ParamField>[m
[32m+[m[32m      </Expandable>[m
[32m+[m[32m    </ParamField>[m
[32m+[m[32m  </Tab>[m
[32m+[m[41m  [m
[32m+[m[32m  <Tab title="Audio Messages">[m
[32m+[m[32m    <ParamField body="audio" type="object" required>[m
[32m+[m[32m      Audio message configuration[m
[32m+[m[32m      <Expandable title="Audio Properties">[m
[32m+[m[32m        <ParamField body="link" type="string" required>[m
[32m+[m[32m          Public URL to the audio file (MP3, AAC, AMR, OGG)[m
[32m+[m[32m        </ParamField>[m
[32m+[m[32m      </Expandable>[m
[32m+[m[32m    </ParamField>[m
[32m+[m[32m  </Tab>[m
[32m+[m[41m  [m
[32m+[m[32m  <Tab title="Document Messages">[m
[32m+[m[32m    <ParamField body="document" type="object" required>[m
[32m+[m[32m      Document message configuration[m
[32m+[m[32m      <Expandable title="Document Properties">[m
[32m+[m[32m        <ParamField body="link" type="string" required>[m
[32m+[m[32m          Public URL to the document file[m
[32m+[m[32m        </ParamField>[m
[32m+[m[32m        <ParamField body="caption" type="string" optional>[m
[32m+[m[32m          Text caption for the document (max 1024 characters)[m
[32m+[m[32m        </ParamField>[m
[32m+[m[32m        <ParamField body="filename" type="string" optional>[m
[32m+[m[32m          Custom filename for the document (with extension)[m
[32m+[m[32m        </ParamField>[m
[32m+[m[32m      </Expandable>[m
[32m+[m[32m    </ParamField>[m
[32m+[m[32m  </Tab>[m
[32m+[m[32m</Tabs>[m
[32m+[m
